            "title": "即月期指開跌175點     低水245點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期開跌175點或0.75%，報23208，較昨日現貨收市低水245點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">科指期貨開跌33點或0.62%，報5254，低水44點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國指期貨開跌62點或0.73%，報8442，低水68點</p>\n</div>",
